@zhubuntu The problem is caused by not exporting Symbol in DLL library. NDArray is explicitly exported in the DLL, that's why the NDArray example works. A quick fix is to modify line 40 of symbolic.h into
<code>
    class MXNET_API Symbol {
</code>
and then recompile libmxnet.dll.

@zhangchen-qinyinghua Can we modify the code so it uses APIs only in the c_api.h? That way we won't need to export the C++ classes and functions one by one.
